{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"grid","mdn_url":"/ko/docs/Web/CSS/grid","locale":"ko","native":"한국어","sidebarHTML":"\n<ol>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS\"><strong>CSS</strong></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Reference\"><strong>CSS Reference</strong></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout\">CSS Grid Layout</a></li>\n <li data-default-state=\"open\"><a href=\"#\"><strong>Guides</strong></a>\n  <ol>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Basic_Concepts_of_Grid_Layout\">Basics concepts of grid layout</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Relationship_of_Grid_Layout\">Relationship to other layout methods</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Line-based_Placement_with_CSS_Grid\">Line-based placement</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Grid_Template_Areas\">Grid template areas</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Layout_using_Named_Grid_Lines\">Layout using named grid lines</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Auto-placement_in_CSS_Grid_Layout\">Auto-placement in grid layout</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Box_Alignment_in_CSS_Grid_Layout\">Box alignment in grid layout</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/CSS_Grid,_Logical_Values_and_Writing_Modes\">Grids, logical values and writing modes</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/CSS_Grid_Layout_and_Accessibility\">CSS Grid Layout and Accessibility</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/CSS_Grid_and_Progressive_Enhancement\">CSS Grid Layout and Progressive Enhancement</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Realizing_common_layouts_using_CSS_Grid_Layout\">Realizing common layouts using grids</a></li>\n  </ol>\n </li>\n <li data-default-state=\"open\"><a href=\"#\"><strong>Properties</strong></a>\n  <ol>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid\">grid</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-area\">grid-area</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-columns\">grid-auto-columns</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-flow\">grid-auto-flow</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-rows\">grid-auto-rows</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-column\">grid-column</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-column-end\">grid-column-end</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-column-gap\">grid-column-gap</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-column-start\">grid-column-start</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-gap\">grid-gap</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-row\">grid-row</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-row-end\">grid-row-end</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-row-gap\">grid-row-gap</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-row-start\">grid-row-start</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template\">grid-template</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-areas\">grid-template-areas</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-columns\">grid-template-columns</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-rows\">grid-template-rows</a></li>\n  </ol>\n </li>\n <li data-default-state=\"open\"><a href=\"#\"><strong>Glossary</strong></a>\n  <ol>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_lines\">Grid lines</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_tracks\">Grid tracks</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_cell\">Grid cell</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_areas\">Grid areas</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Gutters\">Gutters</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_rows\">Grid row</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_column\">Grid column</a></li>\n  </ol>\n </li>\n</ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong><code>grid</code></strong> CSS 속성은&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Shorthand_properties\">shorthand</a> property 입니다. 외재적인 속성인 (<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-rows\"><code>grid-template-rows</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-columns\"><code>grid-template-columns</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-areas\"><code>grid-template-areas</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>), 값과 내재적인 속성인&nbsp;(<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-rows\"><code>grid-auto-rows</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-columns\"><code>grid-auto-columns</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-flow\"><code>grid-auto-flow</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>), 값을 한번에 설정합니다.</p>\n\n<div id=\"sect1\"><iframe class=\"interactive\" height=\"390\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/css/grid.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect2\">\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> You can only specify the explicit <em>or</em> the implicit grid properties in a single <code>grid</code> declaration. The sub-properties you don’t specify are set to their initial value, as normal for shorthands. Also, the gutter properties are NOT reset by this shorthand.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css no-line-numbers notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">/* &lt;'grid-template'&gt; values */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> none<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"a\"</span> 100px <span class=\"token string\">\"b\"</span> 1fr<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> [linename1] <span class=\"token string\">\"a\"</span> 100px [linename2]<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"a\"</span> 200px <span class=\"token string\">\"b\"</span> min-content<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"a\"</span> <span class=\"token function\">minmax</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>100px<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> max-content<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"b\"</span> 20%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100px / 200px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">minmax</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>400px<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> min-content<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> / <span class=\"token function\">repeat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>auto-fill<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 50px<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* &lt;'grid-template-rows'&gt; /\n   [ auto-flow &amp;&amp; dense? ] &lt;'grid-auto-columns'&gt;? values */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 200px / auto-flow<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 30% / auto-flow dense<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">repeat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>3<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> [line1 line2 line3] 200px<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> / auto-flow 300px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> [line1] <span class=\"token function\">minmax</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>20em<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> max-content<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> / auto-flow dense 40%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* [ auto-flow &amp;&amp; dense? ] &lt;'grid-auto-rows'&gt;? /\n   &lt;'grid-template-columns'&gt; values */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> auto-flow / 200px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> auto-flow dense / 30%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> auto-flow 300px / <span class=\"token function\">repeat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>3<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> [line1 line2 line3] 200px<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> auto-flow dense 40% / [line1] <span class=\"token function\">minmax</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>20em<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> max-content<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* Global values */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> inherit<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> initial<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> unset<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"values","title":"Values","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"grid-template\"><code>&lt;'grid-template'&gt;</code></dt>\n <dd><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-columns\"><code>grid-template-columns</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-rows\"><code>grid-template-rows</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-areas\"><code>grid-template-areas</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 값을 내포하고 있는 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template\"><code>grid-template</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>의 값을 정의합니다.</dd>\n <dt id=\"grid-template-rows_auto-flow_dense_grid-auto-columns\"><code>&lt;'grid-template-rows'&gt; / [ auto-flow &amp;&amp; dense? ] &lt;'grid-auto-columns'&gt;?</code></dt>\n <dd><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-rows\"><code>grid-template-rows</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> (and the <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-columns\"><code>grid-template-columns</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> property to&nbsp;<code>none</code>)은 auto-flow 값을 설정합니다. <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-columns\"><code>grid-auto-columns</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> (and setting <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-rows\"><code>grid-auto-rows</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> to&nbsp;<code>auto</code>)은 auto-repeat를 설정합니다. <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-flow\"><code>grid-auto-flow</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 또한 마찬가지로 auto-repeat에 영향을 줍니다. 만약 이 값이 생략되었다면 그 기본값은&nbsp;<code>dense</code>&nbsp;입니다.\n <p><code><font face=\"Verdana, arial, x-locale-body, sans-serif\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\">만약&nbsp;</span></font>grid</code>&nbsp;의 sub-properties가 있다면, 해당 값으로 초기화 됩니다.</p>\n </dd>\n <dt id=\"_auto-flow_dense_grid-auto-rows_grid-template-columns\"><code>[ auto-flow &amp;&amp; dense? ] &lt;'grid-auto-rows'&gt;? / &lt;'grid-template-columns'&gt;</code></dt>\n <dd><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-columns\"><code>grid-template-columns</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> (and the <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-rows\"><code>grid-template-rows</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> property to <code>none</code>)은 auto-flow 값을 설정합니다.&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-rows\"><code>grid-auto-rows</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> (and setting <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-columns\"><code>grid-auto-columns</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> to <code>auto</code>)은 열(row)에 대한 auto-repeat를 설정합니다. <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-flow\"><code>grid-auto-flow</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 또한 마찬가지로 auto-repeat에 영향을 줍니다. 만약 이 값이 생략되었다면 그 기본값은 <code>dense</code>&nbsp;입니다.\n <p><code><font face=\"Verdana, arial, x-locale-body, sans-serif\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\">만약&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></font>grid</code>&nbsp;의 sub-properties가 있다면, 해당 값으로 초기화 됩니다.</p>\n </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"formal_syntax","title":"Formal syntax","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;'grid-template'&gt; (en-US)</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#single_bar\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">| (en-US)</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-rows\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;'grid-template-rows'&gt; (en-US)</a> / <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#brackets\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">[ (en-US)</a> auto-flow <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#double_ampersand\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&amp;&amp; (en-US)</a> dense<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#question_mark\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">? (en-US)</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#brackets\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">] (en-US)</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-columns\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;'grid-auto-columns'&gt; (en-US)</a><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#question_mark\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">? (en-US)</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#single_bar\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">| (en-US)</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#brackets\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">[ (en-US)</a> auto-flow <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#double_ampersand\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&amp;&amp; (en-US)</a> dense<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#question_mark\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">? (en-US)</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#brackets\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">] (en-US)</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-rows\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;'grid-auto-rows'&gt; (en-US)</a><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#question_mark\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">? (en-US)</a> / <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-columns\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;'grid-template-columns'&gt; (en-US)</a></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Example","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"html_content","title":"HTML Content","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>container<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"css_content","title":"CSS Content","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">#container</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> grid<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">repeat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>2<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 60px<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> / auto-flow 80px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">#container &gt; div</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #8ca0ff<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 50px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 50px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"result","title":"Result","isH3":true,"content":"<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Example sample\" id=\"frame_example\" width=\"100%\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/ko/docs/Web/CSS/grid/_sample_.example.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"Specifications","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-grid/#propdef-grid\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Grid Layout<br><small lang=\"ko\">The definition of 'grid' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-cr\">Candidate Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p><table class=\"properties\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/CSS/initial_value\">초기값</a></th><td>as each of the properties of the shorthand:<br><ul><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-rows\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-template-rows (en-US)</a>: <code>none</code></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-columns\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-template-columns (en-US)</a>: <code>none</code></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-areas\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-template-areas (en-US)</a>: <code>none</code></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-rows\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-auto-rows (en-US)</a>: <code>auto</code></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-columns\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-auto-columns (en-US)</a>: <code>auto</code></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-flow\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-auto-flow (en-US)</a>: <code>row</code></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/column-gap\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-column-gap (en-US)</a>: <code>0</code></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/row-gap\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-row-gap (en-US)</a>: <code>0</code></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/column-gap\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">column-gap (en-US)</a>: <code>normal</code></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/row-gap\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">row-gap (en-US)</a>: <code>normal</code></li></ul></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">적용대상</th><td>grid containers</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/CSS/inheritance\">상속</a></th><td>no</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Percentages</th><td>as each of the properties of the shorthand:<br><ul><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-rows\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-template-rows (en-US)</a>: refer to corresponding dimension of the content area</li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-columns\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-template-columns (en-US)</a>: refer to corresponding dimension of the content area</li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-rows\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-auto-rows (en-US)</a>: refer to corresponding dimension of the content area</li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-columns\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-auto-columns (en-US)</a>: refer to corresponding dimension of the content area</li></ul></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/CSS/computed_value\">Computed value</a></th><td>as each of the properties of the shorthand:<br><ul><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-rows\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-template-rows (en-US)</a>: as specified, but with relative lengths converted into absolute lengths</li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-columns\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-template-columns (en-US)</a>: as specified, but with relative lengths converted into absolute lengths</li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-areas\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-template-areas (en-US)</a>: as specified</li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-rows\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-auto-rows (en-US)</a>: the percentage as specified or the absolute length</li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-columns\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-auto-columns (en-US)</a>: the percentage as specified or the absolute length</li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-flow\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-auto-flow (en-US)</a>: as specified</li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/column-gap\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-column-gap (en-US)</a>: the percentage as specified or the absolute length</li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/row-gap\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-row-gap (en-US)</a>: the percentage as specified or the absolute length</li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/column-gap\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">column-gap (en-US)</a>: as specified, with &lt;length&gt;s made absolute, and normal computing to zero except on multi-column elements</li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/row-gap\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">row-gap (en-US)</a>: as specified, with &lt;length&gt;s made absolute, and normal computing to zero except on multi-column elements</li></ul></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Animation type</th><td>discrete</td></tr></tbody></table></p>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"css.properties.grid","dataURL":"/ko/docs/Web/CSS/grid/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Related CSS properties: <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template\"><code>grid-template</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-rows\"><code>grid-template-rows</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-columns\"><code>grid-template-columns</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-areas\"><code>grid-template-areas</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-columns\"><code>grid-auto-columns</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-rows\"><code>grid-auto-rows</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-flow\"><code>grid-auto-flow</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li>Grid Layout Guide: <em><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Line-based_Placement_with_CSS_Grid\">Line-based placement with CSS Grid</a></em></li>\n <li>Grid Layout Guide: <em><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Grid_Template_Areas#grid_definition_shorthands\">Grid template areas - Grid definition shorthands</a></em></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Example","id":"example"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"grid CSS 속성은 shorthand property 입니다. 외재적인 속성인 (grid-template-rows (en-US), grid-template-columns (en-US), grid-template-areas (en-US)), 값과 내재적인 속성인 (grid-auto-rows (en-US), grid-auto-columns (en-US), grid-auto-flow (en-US)), 값을 한번에 설정합니다.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"grid","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"grid","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"grid","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"grid","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"grid","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"grid","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"grid","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"grid","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"grid","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文